  86: ### Consumer 経路 (PR #165 の consumer をそのまま再利用)
  87: 
  88: ```bash
  89: # Vendi semantic
  90: .venv/Scripts/python.exe scripts/m9-c-adopt/compute_baseline_vendi.py \
  91:   --persona kant --shards-glob "data/eval/m9-c-adopt-tier-b-pilot-multiturn/kant_r${r}_run*_stim.duckdb" \
  92:   --kernel semantic --window-size 100 \
  93:   --output ".steering/20260514-m9-c-adopt-pilot-multiturn/tier-b-pilot-multiturn-kant-r${r}-vendi-semantic.json"
  94: 
  95: # Big5 ICC (SGLang LoRA-on)
