 488: ## DA-9 — Marginal pass の取り扱い: CI lower bound NOT cleared → ADOPT-WITH-CHANGES retrain path (Codex HIGH-2 反映)
 489: 
 490: - **判断日時**: 2026-05-13
 491: - **背景**: HIGH-2 で point threshold + CI lower bound + direction の
 492:   3 条件 AND を求められ、point は PASS だが CI lower bound が threshold
 493:   未達のケースの operational stance 必要。
 494: - **決定**:
 495:   - **marginal pass 判定**: 3 条件のうち point + direction PASS だが
 496:     CI lower bound が threshold 未達 (e.g. d point=0.35 だが CI
 497:     lower=0.15) → **ADOPT-WITH-CHANGES verdict**
 498:   - retrain path: 別 PR `feature/m9-c-adopt-retrain-v2` で
 499:     - min_examples を 1000 → 3000 に増 (BIG5-CHAT 1/30 規模に近づける)
 500:     - rank を adopted rank で固定
 501:     - stimulus prompt diversity 改善 (M9-eval P3 で新規 prompt 群追加)
 502:   - retrain 後 Tier B 再評価で CI lower bound clear → ADOPT 確定
 503: - **根拠**:
 504:   - **HIGH-2** (Codex): "point thresholds produce ADOPT-WITH-CHANGES
 505:     unless the CI lower bound also clears the threshold and all metric
 506:     directionality is positive versus no-LoRA baseline"
 507:   - spurious adopt を避けつつ scope 不能を起こさない operational stance
 508: - **棄却**:
 509:   - **strict reject** (3 条件全 PASS でなければ REJECT): retrain cost
 510:     high で iteration 困難
 511:   - **marginal も無条件 adopt**: M9-D で巻き戻しリスク
 512: - **影響**:
 513:   - A-8 verdict 判定の precondition
 514:   - ADOPT-WITH-CHANGES 経路は別 PR `feature/m9-c-adopt-retrain-v2` 起票
