   8: 
   9: ## DA-1 — Rank sweep 範囲 `{4, 8, 16}` + conditional rank=32 tail-sweep + `--max-lora-rank >= 16` (Codex HIGH-1 / MEDIUM-3 反映)
  10: 
  11: - **判断日時**: 2026-05-13
  12: - **背景**: CS-5 留保 (rank=8 continuity hypothesis) を adopt phase で
  13:   empirical closure する必要。v1 では rank ∈ {4, 8, 16, 32} の 24h sweep
  14:   を提案、v2 reimagine では {8, 16} hypothesis-confirm のみで 10h、
  15:   comparison で {4, 8, 16} (18h) を hybrid 候補。Codex HIGH-1 が rank=32
  16:   permanent exclusion を risky と判定、conditional tail-sweep trigger +
  17:   SGLang launch arg `--max-lora-rank >= 16` を要求。
  18: - **決定**:
  19:   - default sweep: `rank ∈ {4, 8, 16}`、compute 18h (G-GEAR overnight × 2-3)
  20:   - **conditional rank=32 tail-sweep trigger** (HIGH-1):
  21:     1. Phase B で rank=16 が **throughput PASS** だが **Vendi / ICC /
  22:        Burrows のいずれか 1+ が threshold 未達** (= signal saturate
  23:        未達) → rank=32 tail-sweep 起動
  24:     2. または rank=8→16 で sharp gain (PLORA-like rank sensitivity)
  25:        観察 → rank=32 tail-sweep 起動
  26:     3. tail-sweep の VRAM peak monitor (`nvidia-smi`) + early abort
  27:        (peak > 14GB で kill)
  28:   - **SGLang launch arg amendment** (HIGH-1): CS-1 の `--max-lora-rank 8`
  29:     を `--max-lora-rank 16` (rank=32 fire 時は `--max-lora-rank 32`) に
  30:     amendment、`docs/runbooks/m9-c-adapter-swap-runbook.md` (DB8) に
  31:     Phase B 開始時の amendment 手順を記載
  32:   - **採用基準** (4 軸 intersection、HIGH-2 反映):
  33:     - Vendi semantic effect size (Cohen's d) point + bootstrap CI lower
  34:       bound > 0、direction = "LoRA-on < no-LoRA"
  35:     - Big5 ICC(C,k) ≥ 0.6 point + CI lower bound ≥ 0.6
  36:     - Burrows Δ reduction ≥ 10% point + CI lower bound > 0
  37:     - bench throughput ≥ 70% baseline ceiling
  38:     - smaller rank 優先
  39: - **根拠**:
  40:   - **HIGH-1** (Codex): "PLORA's Qwen2.5-7B sweep found task-dependent
  41:     optima including rank 32, and P-React reports rank-sensitive
  42:     personality modeling" → rank=32 permanent exclusion は risky
  43:   - LoRA Land (arxiv:2405.00732) は rank=8 を 310 model で採用、
  44:     practical anchor として有効
  45:   - PLORA (openreview:azsnOWy9MZ) で Qwen2.5-7B では task-dependent
  46:     optima rank=16/32 観察
  47:   - P-React (aclanthology:2025.findings-acl.328) で personality modeling
  48:     の rank sensitivity 報告
  49:   - SGLang docs (sgl-project.github.io/advanced_features/lora.html):
  50:     `--max-lora-rank` が serving 時の rank ceiling、rank=16 を実際に
  51:     serving するには amendment 必須
  52: - **棄却**:
  53:   - **rank ∈ {4, 8, 16, 32} 全 sweep** (v1): 24h compute、rank=32 は
  54:     VRAM headroom 圧迫 + cost-benefit poor、conditional re-open で
  55:     十分 (HIGH-1)
  56:   - **rank ∈ {8, 16} hypothesis-confirm のみ** (v2 reimagine): CS-5
  57:     closure 不完全、rank=4 を見ない (smaller adapter で持続性能を
  58:     取れる持続テスト不足)
  59:   - **binary search** (rank=8 → 16 → 12 → 14): PEFT/unsloth default が
  60:     powers-of-2、literature 比較不能
  61: - **影響**:
  62:   - `requirement.md` AC-1 修正済 (rank `{4, 8, 16}` + conditional + arg)
  63:   - `design-final.md` A-1 / 既存 CS-* との整合性確認
  64:   - `docs/runbooks/m9-c-adapter-swap-runbook.md` (DB8) に Phase B 着手
  65:     前 `--max-lora-rank` amendment 手順を別 PR で追加
  66:   - Phase B compute budget: 18h (G-GEAR overnight × 2-3)、tail-sweep
  67:     fire 時 +6h
  68: - **re-open 条件**:
  69:   - rank=8 / 16 全て Tier B persona-discriminative でない (= LoRA 自体
  70:     が機能しない) → CS-5 re-open + DB3 re-arm 検討
  71:   - rank=16 throughput PASS だが Vendi/ICC/Burrows のいずれか未達 →
  72:     rank=32 tail-sweep fire
  73:   - rank=8 → 16 で sharp gain (effect size delta > 0.5) → rank=32
