+### HIGH-1 — Scenario I overclaims identifiability from one protocol change
+
+- **箇所**:
+  - `.steering/20260514-m9-c-adopt-pilot-multiturn/requirement.md:17`
+  - `.steering/20260514-m9-c-adopt-pilot-multiturn/requirement.md:61`
